name: Bulky Depth
description:
Collection : The Unique Ocean 
Travel and road stories , golf and sea stories , growth and watching stories . 
I am very interested in collecting beauties , whatever I think is beautiful .
To remove each of these oysters and travel with that's on my shoulders ,I meditated , stood and watched them , saw the whole beauty in them , and on my fifty-day alone trip to southern Iran , to Qeshm Island , Hengam Island and Hormoz Island ,each of which grew beautiful with me and tens of thousands A Killometer away in the north of Iran , the beautiful city of Rasht has became a work of art called Balky Depth .
this is not just a Photo of a mirror with a decorative frame , this is a part of my beauty soul .
